Plans for 0.5.0
===============

  * Use action grouping in replace_both_texts(...)
  * Raise exceptions instead of returning None or False
  * Get rid of logger?
  * Use relib.NONE instead of None in flags?
  * Spell-check dialog mnemonics
      - Join _Back
      - Join _Forward
  * psyco.profile() vs. psyco.classes: benchmark
  * psyco.classes
      - from psyco.classes import psyobj, class Example(psyobj)
      - Psyco will call psyco.bind for you on all methods
  * Redirect/copy sys.stdout to output window?
      - stdout: file-like object with a write(string) method
      - stdout.write(string): insert to text_buffer and scroll
      - sys.__stdout__.write(...)
      - http://diveintopython.org/scripts_and_streams/stdin_stdout_stderr.html
  * yield: any use for this?
      - http://www.python.org/doc/peps/pep-0255/
      - parser
      - no previous() method
  * Move trantool to po directory... NO!
  * setup.py: clean command?
  * setup.py optimization flag: O1/O2/?
  * Do setup.py install options work? Do they need to work?
      --prefix           OK
      --exec-prefix
      --home
      --install-base
      --install-platbase
      --root
      --install-purelib
      --install-lib
      --install-scripts
      --install-data

